th other chains which affects the user experience of web3 dApps built on different chains.</p><div class=\"flex justify-end mt-10 gap-8\"><div class=\"flex justify-end items-center gap-3\"><svg stroke=\"currentColor\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"0\" viewBox=\"0 0 640 512\" class=\"text-[#bfbfbf] text-[11px]\" height=\"1em\" width=\"1em\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M497.941 225.941L286.059 14.059A48 48 0 0 0 252.118 0H48C21.49 0 0 21.49 0 48v204.118a48 48 0 0 0 14.059 33.941l211.882 211.882c18.744 18.745 49.136 18.746 67.882 0l204.118-204.118c18.745-18.745 18.745-49.137 0-67.882zM112 160c-26.51 0-48-21.49-48-48s21.49-48 48-48 48 21.49 48 48-21.49 48-48 48zm513.941 133.823L421.823 497.941c-18.745 18.745-49.137 18.745-67.882 0l-.36-.36L527.64 323.522c16.999-16.999 26.36-39.6 26.36-63.64s-9.362-46.641-26.36-63.64L331.397 0h48.721a48 48 0 0 1 33.941 14.059l211.882 211.882c18.745 18.745 18.745 49.137 0 67.882z\"></path></svg><ul class=\"text-[#777778] text-[10px] flex gap-2\"><li>web3</li><li>blockchain</li></ul></div></div></div></a><a class=\"w-full md:hover:scale-[1.1] transition\" href=\"/blog/a-non-technical-introduction-to-web3\"><div class=\"bg-[#1b1c21] md:min-h-[250px] h-auto p-8 md:group-hover:opacity-100 rounded-md\"><h3 class=\"text-[20px]\">A non-technical introduction to web3</h3><p class=\"text-[#777778] text-[12px] font-light my-4\">Since the existence of the web on the internet, it has grown through different phases with several advantages and disadvantages, which then brings about the era of web3 to improve and fix some of those disadvantages of the past era, so let’s deep dive a bit into the predecessors of web3.</p><div class=\"flex justify-end mt-10 gap-8\"><div class=\"flex justify-end items-center gap-3\"><svg stroke=\"currentColor\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"0\" viewBox=\"0 0 640 512\" class=\"text-[#bfbfbf] text-[11px]\" height=\"1em\" width=\"1em\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M497.941 225